Target platform
-----------------------------------
Debian or Ubuntu Linux


Prerequisites
-----------------------------------
apt-get install zlib1g-dev
apt-get install libapache2-mod-fcgid
apt-get install libfcgi-dev
apt-get install libmysqlclient15-dev

*this one will be removed in future
get mysqlwrapped, compile and install in a system accessible location
unlike the default
i'll be back with either an alternate solution or details on how to use this library


How to compile
-----------------------------------

A. Get Tamarin
https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Tamarin_Build_Documentation
configure with shell
compile

get asc compiler or compile it
make sure it is in

B. Compile Fcgi Tamarin

copy this fcgishell directory inside tamarin-central


edit tamarin-central/manifest.mk
change line"
$(call RECURSE_DIRS,shell)
to:
$(call RECURSE_DIRS,fcgishell)

run make again in your obj directory

the executable is fcgishell/fcgishell


C. setup your Apache2 http server
make sure you have all needed software installed
enable .htaccess files if it's not already so

copy actionscript-www under your webroot
edit the .htaccess file according to your setup


point your browser to the helo.abc file
